{"metadata":{"name":"Jami At Tirmidhi","section":{"24":"The Book on Clothing"}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":1743,"arabicnumber":1743,"text":"حدثنا قتيبة، حدثنا حاتم بن إسماعيل، عن جعفر بن محمد، عن أبيه، قال كان الحسن والحسين يتختمان في يسارهما ‏.‏ وهذا حديث حسن صحيح ‏.‏","grades":[{"name":"Ahmad Muhammad Shakir","grade":"Sahih Muquf"},{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih Muquf"},{"name":"Bashar Awad Maarouf","grade":"Hasan"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Hasan"}],"reference":{"book":24,"hadith":24}}]}